quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,40,"Jortagol wonnde men jokkay mbilee…ďe …ďen ka diina ma…ď…ďe, si tawii ko kam…ďe fooli Muusaa."
  26,41,"Tuma nde mbilee…ďe …ďen arunoo ka Fir'awna fii yo …ďe foolotir e Muusaa …ďe wi'ani mo: "Yalli no woodani men njo…ďdi jawdi maa…óum teddungal si tawii ko menen fooli Muusaa?""
  26,42,"Fir'awna wi'ani …ďe: "Eyyo, njo…ďdi no woodani on, haray si on foolii mo, on wonay …ďa…ótiniraa…ďe ka am jonnugol on darjaaji …ďamtii…ói"."
  26,43,"Muusaa maakani …ďe tawi ko o hoolii…óo Ballal Alla ngal himo …ďanngina wonndema ko o jogii kon wanaa mbilew: "Li…ďee ko li…ďoton kon immorde e …ďokkoy moo…óon e cawoy moo…óon"."
  26,44,"∆Āe li…ďi …ďokkoy ma…ď…ďe e cawoy ma…ď…ďe koy, …ďe wi'i ka li…ďugol koy: "Sabu manngu Fir'awna ko menen woni fooloo…ďe …ďen, ko Muusaa woni foolaa…óo on"."
  26,45,"Muusaa li…ďi tuggordu makko ndun, ndu waylii mboddi, tawi kayru hindu mo…óa ko …ďe hul…ďiniray-noo kon yim…ďe …ďen immorde e mbilewu ngun."
  26,46,"Tuma nde mbilee…ďe …ďen yi'unoo tuggordu Muusaa ndun hindu mo…óa ko …ďe li…ďi kon immorde e mbilewu ma…ď…ďe …ďe suuyi …ďe sujji."
  26,47,"∆Āe wi'i: "Men gom…óinii Jooma tageefooji ndin fow"."
  26,48,"Jooma Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo …ďe his)."
  26,49,"Fir'awna a√Īiri mbilee…ďe …ďen gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal, o wi'i: "Enee, on gom…óinay mo ko adii mi duŇčanaa- de on …óum?! Pellet, ko Muusaa woni maw…óo moo…óon anndin…óo on on mbilewu ngun. Hari on fow on haldiino fii yaltinngol yim…ďe [saare] Misra nden e nder mayre, kono aray ka anndon ko mi fawata on kon immorde e lepte, mami ta∆īu sanne koyngal mo kala e junngo makko ngun mi luutindirira hakkunde majje ta∆īugol koyngal √Īaamal ngal wonndude e junngo nano ngon maa…óum yunnitugol, mami fetu on sanne on fow moo…óon e julle tamaro, mi accataa hay e gooto e moo…óon"."
  26,50,"Mbilee…ďe …ďen wi'ani Fir'awna: "Tanaa alaa e kon ko kammbirantaa men ta∆īugol e fetugol ka aduna, lepte maa…óen iway, menen ko faade ka Joomi amen men ruttotoo, aray O naadoya men ka Yurmeende Makko Duumotoonde."
  26,51,"Menen me…óen jortii nde Alla montanta men goopi amen fe∆ī∆īu…ói …ói men wa…ó…óitii …óum; sabu men wonii adii…ďe gom…óinnde Muusaa goongina mo."
  26,52,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa Yamirgol mo yo o ro∆īidu e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen jemma. Pellet, Fir'awna e wonndu…ďe e makko …ďen …ďe jokkitay …ďe fii yo …ďe artir …ďe."
  26,53,"Fir'awna nuli yoga e konunkee…ďe makko …ďen ka ca'e moo…ďoo…ďe hi…ďe moo…ďa konu ngun fii yo …ďe ruttu …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen nde o anndunoo yaltugol ma…ď…ďe Misra."
  26,54,"Fir'awna wi'i ka fam…óinngol fiyaake …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen: "Pellet, …ďee ko …ďe fedde fam…óunde"."
  26,55,"Pellet, kam…ďe hi…ďe wa…óude ko men tikkiranta …ďe."
  26,56,"Enen non ko en hebilanii…ďe …ďe, ko en finu…ďe."
  26,57,"Men yaltini Fir'awna e yim…ďe makko …ďen ka leydi Misra joomiraari gese al…óu…óe, e can…ói ilooji ndiyam."
  26,58,"E joomiraare ngaluuji jawdi, e ko…óan…óe mo∆ī∆īe."
  26,59,"Ko wano Men yaltiniri nii Fir'awna e yim…ďe makko …ďen e …óii neemaaji, Men wa…óani noone …óii neemaaji …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen ka leydi Saami."
  26,60,"Fir'awna e yim…ďe mu'un …ďen yahi e batte [teppe] …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen ka waqtu pu…óal naange."